songs.title: Uno
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1: Nasty_C]
This might be a little too sudden but
I think you the one for me
I’m thinking bout all of the habits
I’ll pro’bly abandon if you keep me company
You say that your nigga’s the one for you
What’s the scariest thing that he’s done for you?
You say he’s the one, you gon’ take to your mother
He’s one like no other well come and see

[Refrain]
I don't think he’s the one
Trust me he’s not the one
You know I keep it one, hunnit
I don’t think he’s the one
I’ll try that again

[Hook]
I don’t think he’s the one (I don’t think he’s the one)
Trust me he’s not the one (Trust me he’s not the one)
You know I keep it one (I keep it one), hunnit (Hunnit)
I don’t think he’s the one (I don’t think he’s the one)

[Verse 2: Nasty_C]
Maybe I just don’t get it
Cause I’ve just been livin’ the fast life
I’m TBT’ing with my last nights pictures
But am proud of my bad side
Young lady I got that ass tight
And you know I’m selfish with your assets
I just puff and never pass it
Everyone of them moments ever lasting
Long as I still make you happy girl

[Refrain]
He’s not the one
Trust me he’s not the one
You know I keep it one, hunnit
I don’t think he’s the one
I’ll try that again

[Hook]
I don’t think he’s the one (I don’t think he’s the one)
Trust me he’s not the one (Trust me he’s not the one)
You know I keep it one (I keep it one), hunnit (Hunnit)
I don’t think he’s the one (I don’t think he’s the one)

[Verse 3: Tellaman]
(Tellaman, Tellaman ohhh)
That motherfucker is my foe
And he's fucking with your flow
If you wanna take it slow
So write me, let me know
Fuck all the tantrums you throw
It's about time you let me know
About umjita who's making you blow
And he's just an average Joe
You've been on my mind, mind
It's like I saw your name up on the skyline
And even though I won't get on a knee for ya
You can trust that I've got honesty for ya
Got what you need for ya
Shit is a breeze for ya
I swear to god I would even learn how to roll weed for ya
I swear to god I'd even cause an Oscar winning scene for ya
Di Caprio dreams for ya (for ya)
I pledge my allegiance from morning to evening
Do you know the meaning?
I've got what you're seeking
He ain't got the vision
That mjita is creeping
So when he breaks your heart, girl I'll pick up the pieces
'Cause he ain't the one
No, no he ain't the one
Baby girl he ain't the one
No, no he ain't the one
No, no
